title: Opentrons Logo Protocol
author: Opentrons
description:
This is a demonstration protocol so you can get familiar with your
robot. All you need is some food dye and a trough!
time-estimate: 2-5 minutes depending on pipette model chosen
process:
Choose your pipette type (located on the right mount) and the location of the dyes
Add two different dyes in a 12 column trough
Upload your Logo protocol and hit run!
